      • createStudent

        @PostMapping("/students/create")
public String createStudent​(@Valid
                            @Valid Student s,
                            org.springframework.validation.BindingResult resultS,
                            @Valid
                            @Valid Address a,
                            org.springframework.validation.BindingResult resultA,
                            @RequestParam(value="courseids[]",defaultValue="")
                            List<Long> courseids)
        This controller method handles requests to "/students/create". Therefore it handles student object creation.
        Parameters:
        s - The Student object to be persisted.
        resultS - The BindingResults used for validation of the Student object.
        a - The Address object attached to the Student to be persisted.
        resultA - The BindingResult used for Validation of the Address object.
        courseids - The courses associated to the given Student object.
        Returns:
        A redirect to "/", which shows the list of all students.

public String findStudents​(org.springframework.ui.Model model,
                           @RequestParam(defaultValue="")
                           String search,
                           @RequestParam(defaultValue="0")
                           int page)
